  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "1. 概要：座舱系统的仪表侧支持一些提示类或报警类的信息展示，简称Warning，这些信息给与驾驶员指导性操作或提示故障及风险；"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "2. 需求文档："
    },
    {
      "type": "code_block",
      "language": "",
      "content": "PIS-2062 Cluster Telltale Requirement.docx"
    },
    {
      "type": "code_block",
      "language": "",
      "content": "PIS-2047_EngineeringMode.docx"
    },
    {
      "type": "code_block",
      "language": "",
      "content": "PIS-2076 Cluster General Requirement.docx"
    },
    {
      "type": "code_block",
      "language": "",
      "content": "PIS-2085 IPC SW Specification V3.1.docx"
    },
    {
      "type": "code_block",
      "language": "",
      "content": "……"
    },
    {
      "type": "code_block",
      "language": "",
      "content": "Warning列表：PIS-2069 Cluster Warning Requirement(effect ICS&HUD).xlsx"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "（以客户最新为准）"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "3. 模块分析："
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "3.1. Warning集合介绍："
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "目前分析是两大类（有变更后续在补充）"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "第一类：根据电源状态控制，PM RUN Property = \"Yes\"，电源切换由RUN切换到ACC、OFF时，不再提示；"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "第二类：不受电源状态影响，PM RUN Property = \"No\"，电源切换到非RUN，也会判定提示；"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "还有个特殊的子集，某些Warning有延时处理的逻辑需求，有个单独的Mapping表，在周期性任务中会判定超时，再进一步处理；"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "代码中：用Warning ID的区间，进行了种类的区分；"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/SWC_OCD_Warnings_Telltales_SRC/image-2024-8-27_13-52-52.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/SWC_OCD_Warnings_Telltales_SRC/image-2024-8-27_13-52-52.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "非can总线信号触发的Warning："
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "CLEA部分：Warning #9601-9604"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "GB部分：Warning #8001 -8002 / Warning #8100+(GB L2++项目Only)"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "3.2. Warning提示种类："
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "headers": [
        "",
        ""
      ],
      "rows": [
        [
          "Chime音效",
          "Chime ID - 0 不需要触发Chime Chime ID - 具体数值标明Warning触发的Chime的ID"
        ],
        [
          "显示在HUD",
          "抬头显示，此项紧CLEA适用？？"
        ],
        [
          "显示在IPC上",
          "仪表"
        ],
        [
          "显示在ICS上",
          "中控"
        ],
        [
          "",
          ""
        ]
      ]
    },
